    "name": "execution",
    "purpose": "Owns the execution protocol relocated from the former execution.rs flat file into per-concern files. event.rs defines the ExecutionEvent stream enum (PreviewQuery/Preview/Evoke/Query/Cancel/Kill/Status/Update) that carries ToolPreview values, an ExecutionRequest, an ExecutionStatus, or an ExecutionUpdate, plus the ExecutionUpdate content payload and the ExecutionRequest carrying an ExecutionSignature with prompt, an optional raw tool_request string, and user_options; signature.rs defines the ExecutionSignature record of task_id/exe_id/name; status.rs defines the ExecutionStatus lifecycle enum Started/Running/Canceled/Killed/Succeed/Failed. mod.rs is namespace and re-export wiring only.",
